# Lumapps SDK

<p style="text-align:center">
    <a href="https://github.com/lumapps/lumapps-sdk/actions?query=workflow%3ACI"><img alt="Action Status" src="https://github.com/lumapps/lumapps-sdk/workflows/CI/badge.svg"></a>
